1
00:00:36,930 --> 00:00:42,320
=Loving The Lie=

2
00:00:42,360 --> 00:00:45,330
=Episode 13=

3
00:00:53,300 --> 00:00:54,819
What is this secret place?

4
00:00:54,820 --> 00:00:56,019
Why do I need to be blindfolded?

5
00:00:56,020 --> 00:00:56,979
Don't worry.

6
00:00:56,980 --> 00:00:58,499
I won't lead you to any harm.

7
00:00:58,500 --> 00:00:59,299
It's a surprise.

8
00:00:59,300 --> 00:01:00,019
We're almost there.

9
00:01:00,020 --> 00:01:01,299
What is it?

10
00:01:01,300 --> 00:01:02,330
Stop.

11
00:01:02,700 --> 00:01:03,339
We're here?

12
00:01:03,340 --> 00:01:04,130
Yes.

13
00:01:16,940 --> 00:01:19,450
This is a private art exhibition
I organized just for you.

14
00:01:29,572 --> 00:01:32,752
♪When love is getting out of hand♪

15
00:01:33,720 --> 00:01:37,000
♪When your hands become gentle♪

16
00:01:37,362 --> 00:01:39,639
♪When you say you love me♪

17
00:01:39,640 --> 00:01:43,558
♪Staring at me with that silly look♪

18
00:01:43,830 --> 00:01:46,219
♪Suddenly, you turn and walk away♪

19
00:01:46,220 --> 00:01:49,727
♪Looking at the gentleness you gave me♪

20
00:01:50,270 --> 00:01:53,469
♪The loneliness when you're away♪

21
00:01:54,380 --> 00:01:55,530
What do you think?

22
00:01:56,860 --> 00:01:58,930
Organized by yours truly, Guan Huai.

23
00:02:02,820 --> 00:02:04,299
And two guest curators.

24
00:02:04,300 --> 00:02:05,259
The uninvited

25
00:02:05,260 --> 00:02:07,419
Guan Xin,

26
00:02:07,420 --> 00:02:09,259
and her nosy little sidekick,

27
00:02:09,260 --> 00:02:10,226
Qin Shen.

28
00:02:11,780 --> 00:02:12,819
Congratulations.

29
00:02:12,820 --> 00:02:13,970
Thank you.

30
00:02:14,820 --> 00:02:15,970
You're welcome.

31
00:02:18,940 --> 00:02:21,170
You don't mind us
crashing the party, do you?

32
00:02:21,620 --> 00:02:22,779
Not at all.

33
00:02:22,780 --> 00:02:24,694
I should be the one
thanking you for coming.

34
00:02:24,695 --> 00:02:27,231
♪Every glance I steal
is filled with tenderness♪

35
00:02:27,232 --> 00:02:29,459
♪You are the blooming flower♪

36
00:02:29,460 --> 00:02:31,699
I'm probably the last person

37
00:02:31,700 --> 00:02:33,250
to know about this exhibit.

38
00:02:34,447 --> 00:02:37,865
♪So I'll walk beside you, hand in hand♪

39
00:02:37,866 --> 00:02:39,903
♪Never letting go♪

40
00:02:39,904 --> 00:02:42,499
I had even forgotten

41
00:02:42,500 --> 00:02:44,185
where I kept some of these paintings.

42
00:02:44,186 --> 00:02:46,813
♪No matter where you are♪

43
00:02:46,814 --> 00:02:50,524
♪I'm ready to go♪

44
00:02:51,740 --> 00:02:53,410
Let's save the tears for later.

45
00:02:53,460 --> 00:02:54,610
I'll hold that for you.

46
00:02:55,300 --> 00:02:56,939
There's a special event coming up.

47
00:02:56,940 --> 00:03:00,490
It's time for our featured activity.

48
00:03:02,140 --> 00:03:03,690
Featured activity?

49
00:03:05,140 --> 00:03:09,391
Let's have our great artist,
Xin Yi, to paint live.

50
00:03:09,392 --> 00:03:13,142
♪When you appeared in my world♪

51
00:03:13,143 --> 00:03:16,604
♪You became the axis of time itself♪

52
00:03:16,811 --> 00:03:22,779
♪With your pure and gentle heart,
you froze the world in a perfect moment♪

53
00:03:22,780 --> 00:03:24,807
This is a unique form of expression.

54
00:03:24,808 --> 00:03:27,489
♪I just want to hold your hand♪

55
00:03:27,490 --> 00:03:28,469
♪No need to look back♪

56
00:03:28,470 --> 00:03:29,598
Surprisingly therapeutic too.

57
00:03:29,599 --> 00:03:32,539
♪Every glance I steal
is filled with tenderness♪

58
00:03:32,540 --> 00:03:33,339
Here you go.

59
00:03:33,340 --> 00:03:34,139
You're out of blue.

60
00:03:34,140 --> 00:03:35,450
Try the red.

61
00:03:36,325 --> 00:03:40,482
♪Warming my world with your light♪

62
00:03:40,550 --> 00:03:43,539
♪So I'll walk beside you, hand in hand♪

63
00:03:43,540 --> 00:03:45,539
(After that incident all those years ago,)

64
00:03:45,540 --> 00:03:46,779
(painting became)

65
00:03:46,780 --> 00:03:49,170
(a tool for revenge.)

66
00:03:49,180 --> 00:03:50,499
(Over time,)

67
00:03:50,500 --> 00:03:52,419
(my dreams got buried in dust.)

68
00:03:52,420 --> 00:03:55,330
(My passion faded away.)

69
00:03:55,740 --> 00:03:56,930
(But in this moment,)

70
00:03:56,980 --> 00:03:58,699
(I finally remembered)

71
00:03:58,700 --> 00:04:00,890
(I picked up a brush)

72
00:04:01,260 --> 00:04:02,662
(because of my love for art.)

73
00:04:02,663 --> 00:04:06,537
♪My heart clears and shines♪

74
00:04:06,538 --> 00:04:10,299
♪Colored by the rainbow you drew♪

75
00:04:10,300 --> 00:04:10,899
Oops!

76
00:04:10,900 --> 00:04:12,299
Let me paint something too.

77
00:04:12,300 --> 00:04:12,979
Guan Huai!

78
00:04:12,980 --> 00:04:13,659
Careful!

79
00:04:13,660 --> 00:04:15,219
I'm wearing white!

80
00:04:15,220 --> 00:04:15,979
Don't be so fussy,

81
00:04:15,980 --> 00:04:16,659
Xin.

82
00:04:16,660 --> 00:04:19,444
Clothes are meant to be dirtied.

83
00:04:19,445 --> 00:04:20,451
I'm not the canvas!

84
00:04:20,452 --> 00:04:21,684
Don't paint on me.

85
00:04:21,685 --> 00:04:22,899
♪No need to look back♪

86
00:04:22,900 --> 00:04:24,579
Why not?

87
00:04:24,580 --> 00:04:25,259
Look.

88
00:04:25,260 --> 00:04:27,099
Now we're both part of the painting.

89
00:04:27,100 --> 00:04:27,859
What do you think?

90
00:04:27,860 --> 00:04:29,459
Poetic, right?

91
00:04:29,460 --> 00:04:30,259
Guan Huai!

92
00:04:30,260 --> 00:04:31,739
You're asking for it now!

93
00:04:31,740 --> 00:04:33,170
You're bold, huh? I'm warning you!

94
00:04:33,340 --> 00:04:34,859
- Come here!
- I'm not a kid anymore!

95
00:04:34,860 --> 00:04:35,259
Come here!

96
00:04:35,260 --> 00:04:35,939
Stay back!

97
00:04:35,940 --> 00:04:36,730
Guan Huai!

98
00:04:37,780 --> 00:04:39,659
- Don't run!
- I'm the Monkey King!

99
00:04:39,660 --> 00:04:40,567
You'll never catch me!

100
00:04:40,568 --> 00:04:42,899
♪Giving you all that I am♪

101
00:04:42,900 --> 00:04:44,059
Stop right there!

102
00:04:44,060 --> 00:04:44,585
Hey!

103
00:04:44,586 --> 00:04:46,899
♪No matter where you are♪

104
00:04:46,900 --> 00:04:50,038
♪I'm ready to go♪

105
00:04:57,860 --> 00:04:58,930
Catch me if you can!

106
00:05:11,260 --> 00:05:12,090
Stop right there!

107
00:05:18,220 --> 00:05:20,939
Xin. Couldn't you have gone
a little easier on me?

108
00:05:20,940 --> 00:05:22,099
Look what you splashed on me.

109
00:05:22,100 --> 00:05:23,560
You're one to talk.

110
00:05:23,560 --> 00:05:26,280
Look at this. I've got a meeting after this.
I can't show up like this.

111
00:05:26,280 --> 00:05:26,939
Oh, relax.

112
00:05:26,940 --> 00:05:29,210
I already booked us a hotel
at the foot of the mountain.

113
00:05:29,260 --> 00:05:32,010
I wouldn't let you walk around
looking like this. Let's go wash up.

114
00:05:34,740 --> 00:05:35,730
You brat!

115
00:05:35,740 --> 00:05:36,890
Get back here!

116
00:05:37,100 --> 00:05:40,010
You seem happy today.

117
00:05:41,740 --> 00:05:44,099
Hosting an art exhibit
was my childhood dream.

118
00:05:44,100 --> 00:05:46,730
I never thought
it would actually come true.

119
00:05:49,660 --> 00:05:51,640
It's been a while
since I've seen you smile like this.

120
00:05:51,980 --> 00:05:54,570
Not since that incident.

121
00:05:59,900 --> 00:06:01,370
Is it because of Guan Huai?

122
00:06:07,140 --> 00:06:08,290
Xin Yi.

123
00:06:09,860 --> 00:06:11,570
Are you falling for him?

124
00:06:19,860 --> 00:06:21,299
I know who he is.

125
00:06:21,300 --> 00:06:23,610
I'd never fall for my enemy.

126
00:06:28,940 --> 00:06:30,770
What's the hurry?

127
00:06:32,260 --> 00:06:34,499
The exhibit might be over,

128
00:06:34,500 --> 00:06:35,339
but I've got

129
00:06:35,340 --> 00:06:37,370
one more surprise for you.

130
00:06:38,100 --> 00:06:39,250
After you.

131
00:07:11,500 --> 00:07:12,499
(When I grow up,)

132
00:07:12,500 --> 00:07:15,579
(I want to build a candy wrapper house.)

133
00:07:15,580 --> 00:07:16,379
(My daddy said)

134
00:07:16,380 --> 00:07:17,859
(you can have)

135
00:07:17,860 --> 00:07:19,930
(the sweetest dreams inside one.)

136
00:07:44,700 --> 00:07:45,850
What do you think?

137
00:07:46,660 --> 00:07:48,179
I ate eight cans of candy in a day

138
00:07:48,180 --> 00:07:49,730
just to collect all this for you.

139
00:07:51,140 --> 00:07:54,170
The candy house didn't work out,

140
00:07:54,340 --> 00:07:56,450
but this candy tent isn't half bad,
right?

141
00:07:58,140 --> 00:08:00,139
It might be a little drafty,

142
00:08:00,140 --> 00:08:01,770
but it comes with its own speakers.

143
00:08:01,900 --> 00:08:03,050
Listen.

144
00:08:14,860 --> 00:08:17,570
You really were a dreamer as a kid.

145
00:08:17,620 --> 00:08:18,859
But that's okay.

146
00:08:18,860 --> 00:08:20,210
Whatever you can imagine,

147
00:08:20,620 --> 00:08:22,170
I'll make it real.

148
00:08:23,860 --> 00:08:25,010
Why?

149
00:08:25,380 --> 00:08:26,659
Why what?

150
00:08:26,660 --> 00:08:28,570
Why are you doing all this?

151
00:08:30,180 --> 00:08:32,130
Why are you being so nice to me?

152
00:08:45,100 --> 00:08:46,539
Do we always need a reason?

153
00:08:46,540 --> 00:08:48,499
Just think of it as an act of kindness.

154
00:08:48,500 --> 00:08:49,570
Okay?

155
00:08:50,980 --> 00:08:53,068
There's no such thing as a free lunch.

156
00:08:53,069 --> 00:08:54,139
♪Your soulful eyes♪

157
00:08:54,140 --> 00:08:56,410
I don't believe you're that selfless.

158
00:08:58,780 --> 00:09:00,770
You do know me pretty well.

159
00:09:01,420 --> 00:09:02,499
But

160
00:09:02,500 --> 00:09:03,730
I just wanted

161
00:09:04,140 --> 00:09:05,920
to make you happy.

162
00:09:05,920 --> 00:09:08,400
Although, I wouldn't mind
a little something in return.

163
00:09:13,178 --> 00:09:18,718
♪Watching the kites fly in the blue sky♪

164
00:09:18,719 --> 00:09:20,526
