166
00:09:23,647 --> 00:09:28,263
♪To relive those moments♪

167
00:09:28,452 --> 00:09:35,419
♪To hold that day once more♪

168
00:09:36,118 --> 00:09:38,647
♪These hopes I whisper in my heart♪

169
00:09:38,648 --> 00:09:39,563
Stingy.

170
